- **Structural**: all 7 docs exist; no `{FILL IN` markers; no `[PROJECT_NAME] Constitution` stub
- **Scenario fidelity**: every principle has a scenario; â‰Ą3 negative assertions per scenario; behavioral variation; filmable success; Validation Matrix with empty "Uncovered Assertions" and "Tasks Without Assertions" rows; "Why this matters" quantified
